{EX LIFE} (As you put this creature, shieldify the top card of your deck. When this creature would leave, put that shield into your graveyard instead.)
{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, look at the top 4 cards of your deck. Put any number of multicolored creatures that have total cost 9 or less. Put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.
